tic mechanisms to the coherence state of\nthe system. We show that the transmission delay is a necessary condition for\nsymmetry breaking, i.e. a non-symmetric phase lag between the macroscopic\noscillations, potentially giving an explanation to the experimentally observed\nvariety of gamma phase-locking modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Dec 2018 10:26:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
