rs, irrespective of the programming language used.\nFurthermore, we deploy ICSREF on a commercial smartphone which orchestrates and\nlaunches a completely automated process-aware attack against a chemical process\ntestbed. This example of dynamic payload generation showcases how ICSREF can\nenable sophisticated attacks without any prior knowledge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Dec 2018 12:58:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-20"}
